## CRITICAL BUG FOUND: Role Priority Lists
- _ALIGNER_PRIORITY = (4, 5, 6, 7, 3) — only agent 3 could be aligner in 4-agent mode!
- _SCRAMBLER_PRIORITY = (7, 6) — no agent 0-3 could be scrambler!
- Tournament uses 4 agents per team (IDs 0-3), so ALL agents were miners
- This explains why tournament scores were terrible
- Fix: reorder priorities to (0, 1, 2, ..., 7) for aligners, (3, 7, 6, 2) for scramblers
- Also added num_agents-aware pressure budget capping

